Download TIGER Shapes for Area Water

Source: R/area_water.R
tt_area_water.Rd

Download TIGER Shapes for Area Water

Usage

tt_area_water(state, county, year = 2021)

Arguments

state

FIPs, postal codes, or full name of states.

county

FIPs codes or full name of counties. Optional.

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_area_water('DE')
